The [[Stub Resolver]] is the software component on the [[Client]] side that just sends any and all [[DNS Queries|DNS Query]] to a pre-configured [[Recursive Resolver Server|Recursive Resolver]] (with the [[Recursion Desired Flag]] set), getting [[said server|Recursive Resolver Server]] do all the work and then just using the [[response|DNS Response]] from [[said server|Recursive Resolver]].

